---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - LastWave"
  description="Learn about LastWave, the free tool that turns your Last.fm and ListenBrainz scrobbles into stunning wave visualizations of your music listening trends."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6">
    <h1 class="text-lw-heading mt-10 mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">What is LastWave?</h1>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      LastWave is a free tool that visualizes your music listening history as a beautiful wave
      graph. Connect your <a
        href="https://last.fm"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">Last.fm</a
      >
      or <a
        href="https://listenbrainz.org"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">ListenBrainz</a
      >
      account to see your top artists, albums, and genres charted over time — the more you listen to an
      artist, the larger their wave on the graph.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lw-muted mt-4 leading-relaxed">
      Use Spotify, Apple Music, or another streaming service? You can connect it to
      <a href="https://last.fm" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors"
        >Last.fm</a
      >
      to start tracking your listening history, then visualize it here with LastWave.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lw-heading mt-10 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Who built LastWave?</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      LastWave is written and maintained by <a
        href="https://savas.ca/"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">Niko Savas</a
      >. Swing by my
      <a
        href="http://last.fm/user/taurheim"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">last.fm</a
      > profile and say hi!
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lw-heading mt-10 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Support LastWave</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      Any money donated will go directly to hosting and server costs for LastWave, so that I can
      keep LastWave completely free!
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      <a
        href="https://buymeacoffee.com/nikosavas"
        class="bg-lw-accent text-lw-bg hover:bg-lw-accent-dim inline-block rounded-lg px-6 py-2 text-sm tracking-wider uppercase transition-all"
        >Buy me a coffee</a
      >
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lw-heading mt-10 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Contribute</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted leading-relaxed">
      If you're a developer who wants a feature or wants to help develop this tool, please swing by
      this project's
      <a
        href="https://github.com/taurheim/LastWave"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">GitHub repository</a
      > and submit a pull request!
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lw-heading mt-10 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Technologies</h2>
    <p class="text-lw-muted mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Version 4 of LastWave is built using <a
        href="https://astro.build/"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">Astro</a
      >,
      <a href="https://react.dev/" class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors"
        >React</a
      >, and
      <a
        href="https://www.typescriptlang.org"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">TypeScript</a
      >. For a full list of dependencies, visit the project's
      <a
        href="https://github.com/taurheim/LastWave"
        class="text-lw-accent hover:text-lw-accent-dim transition-colors">GitHub</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
